<template><div><h1 id="_11-一套最舒适的开发环境" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_11-一套最舒适的开发环境"><span>11.一套最舒适的开发环境</span></a></h1>
<p>一套最舒适 最好的开发环境应该是什么样子的呢？</p>
<h2 id="windows" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#windows"><span>Windows</span></a></h2>
<ol>
<li>将系统更新到最新，包括驱动等</li>
<li>将系统归属地改为香港，设定好时间日期格式(设定为香港可以访问到更多有趣的内容)</li>
<li>在系统设置中配置好 <strong>开发者选项</strong></li>
<li>配置好 <a href="/tutorial/proxy_wall_ready.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">翻墙和代理服务</a></li>
<li>安装 <a href="https://www.google.com/chrome/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Chrome</a></li>
<li>安装并配置 <a href="/tools/git/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Git</a></li>
<li>安装并配置 <a href="/tools/vscode/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">VSCode</a></li>
<li>安装并配置 <a href="/tutorial/wsl_ready.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WSL</a></li>
<li>设定好 <a href="/tutorial/wsl_proxy.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WSL 的系统代理</a></li>
<li>然后在 WSL 中像 <a href="/developer/linux/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Linux</a> 一样去使用 Windows 进行开发和编码</li>
<li>安装并设置 <a href="/tools/uTools.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">uTools</a></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="macos" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#macos"><span>macOS</span></a></h2>
<ol>
<li>检查系统更新</li>
<li>系统常规性设置，比如 <a href="https://support.apple.com/zh-cn/guide/mac-help/mchlp2304/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">在 Mac 上显示或隐藏文件扩展名</a></li>
<li>配置好 <a href="/tutorial/proxy_wall_ready.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">翻墙和代理服务</a></li>
<li>安装 <a href="https://www.google.com/chrome/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Chrome</a></li>
<li>检查并配置好 <a href="https://support.apple.com/zh-cn/guide/terminal/welcome/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Terminal</a>，并安装 <a href="https://sysin.org/blog/macos-zsh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">oh-my-zsh </a></li>
<li>安装 <a href="https://brew.sh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Homebrew</a></li>
<li>检查并配置 <a href="/tools/git/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Git</a> 等常用命令</li>
<li>安装并配置 <a href="/tools/vscode/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">VSCode</a></li>
<li>安装并设置 <a href="/tools/uTools.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">uTools</a></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="linux" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#linux"><span>Linux</span></a></h2>
<p><a href="/developer/linux/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">墨七编写的 Linux 系列文档</a></p>
</div></template>


